      class="bg-purple-700 text-white text-center py-6 px-4 md:px-12 rounded-lg"
    >
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl font-medium">
        Jack's photograph <em>"The Sound of Speed"</em> has been selected for
        <a
          href="https://www.exhibizone.com/p/future2025.html?TP=artworks&AWID=2440602000241869204"
          class="underline hover:text-blue-200 transition-colors"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <em>Future 2025</em>
        </a>, an international online exhibition showcasing visionary artwork
        exploring what lies ahead.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

